				<td colspan="2"><span>Started playing a friends 33 Bard and before I knew it I am a hair from 39 and was wondering can I equip a weapon as well as an instrument or 2 instruments and still be able to get the mods for the instruments. Thank you for any help on this matter ....
<br />

<br />
The Ratt</span></td>
