				<td colspan="2"><span>Learn to twist your instruments.  It's an art that's essentially lost once you go epic, but to me it's the mark of a good bard.  Go to the guides section to learn how to do this.
<br />

<br />
At one point, when I filled the roll of recruitment officer of a guild, I wouldn't admit a bard that couldn't twist instruments.
<br />

<br />
Dlan
